{"tid":204562,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我想搵兩套動漫","createTime":"2017-04-17T07:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T21:23:38.000Z","uid":106044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c20bd1227c1da873ef777a59ba6ffca89f642fa","tid":204562,"uid":106044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T07:11:02.000Z","msg":"第一套我記得以前細個係電視睇嘅，<br />\n有一part好深刻嘅係有個女仔男朋友死左，<br />\n然後有個人幫何男朋友復活，<br />\n但個女朋友從此之後都只可以係個幕後面同佢男朋友傾計，<br />\n點知後尾發現個男朋友冇比人復活到仲變左做隻雀<br />\n呢套野搞到我有童年陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二套係講有個黑色嘅波可以令世界末日嘅<br />\n之後最記得係入面有隻好似獅子咁嘅可愛嘅人物<br />\n<br />\n求各位大大幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d534a81f07f7dbd162ad6c52e4c2d54d0480924f","tid":204562,"uid":93394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T07:19:26.000Z","msg":"1.鋼鍊"},{"pid":"317aa70c77094881f4aa78b0bfa4eabb89bcc2c0","tid":204562,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T19:05:20.000Z","msg":"2.keroro軍曹"},{"pid":"29cb1bacf03eb8419242a25053cf6f30e7a5162d","tid":204562,"uid":62040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T20:31:44.000Z","msg":"鳩估第二套係死神bleach"},{"pid":"ed8b8d2f8bc06f130230472b146ecfbb3b61a36f","tid":204562,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T20:38:17.000Z","msg":"黑球"},{"pid":"f21d528598b8704ee722668a4ba5c26e6464d8e1","tid":204562,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T20:58:12.000Z","msg":"超神傳說"},{"pid":"0a03333517481008731764178a4e140cc8e398ec","tid":204562,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T21:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.鋼鍊</blockquote><br />\n屌你係咪鳩估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"